Package gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppConfig
    Connects the user interface to the service - providing a way for the front end to act with the backend.
    Start
    Start screen - the first screen that the user is brought to.
    StudentClassDashboard
    Student Class Dashboard - displays information about the selected course that the student is enrolled in: Course name # of lates # of absences Teacher name Teacher email Average in the course .
    StudentDashboard
    Main screen for the student - displays general information about the student: Student name Student number Net score Total # of lates Total # of absences # of clubs and volunteer hours
    StudentLogin
    Student login screen
    TeacherAssignmentDashboard
    Teacher Assignment Dashboard - allows teacher to view assignments for the course, as well as update or add assessments
    TeacherClassDashboard
    Teacher Class Dashboard - allows teacher to view information about a course he/she is teaching, take attendance, and enter other screens relating to the course (edit marks and assessments)
    TeacherDashboard
    Teacher Dashboard - main screen for teachers - displays information about all of their students, and all of the courses that he/she teaches
    TeacherLogin
    Teacher login - screen for teacher to log in
    TeacherMarkDashboard
    Teacher Mark Dashboard - screen that allows teacher's to update/add marks for her students under different assignments
